Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.17,0:02:11.59,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you　痛みでさえ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.84,0:02:13.38,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.18,0:02:25.77,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}傷を負った　世界を知った
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.48,0:02:30.73,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}強く儚い果実
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.86,0:02:37.70,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}つきまとう　責任の重たさで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.99,0:02:42.16,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}熟れ落ちて　土へと還る
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.54,0:02:45.08,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you　痛みでさえ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.22,0:02:47.93,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you　通じ合えば
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.06,0:02:52.09,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}この血の滾りを解放してけ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.09,0:02:53.19,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}そこにいますか？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.27,0:02:58.07,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}衝突に戦々恐々　降り立つ堕天使
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.57,0:03:03.32,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}早々に早熟な実も　食らい尽くすの？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.85,0:03:08.98,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}もがく度に　蒼穹に聴いた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.15,0:03:12.15,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}君を確かめた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.15,0:03:12.98,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}あっけない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.98,0:03:16.88,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}無い無い　馴れ合い　有り余った慟哭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.32,0:03:22.16,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}葛藤に混乱していく　今を生きて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.41,0:03:29.00,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)\pos(960,3)}それでもまだ　僕らは目指した
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.06,0:03:30.64,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)\fs45\pos(960,54)}Follow me Follow you　痛みでさえ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.64,0:03:33.27,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you　通じ合えば
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.27,0:03:35.98,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you　何処まででも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:37.44,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,300)}Follow me Follow you
